{"tid":2401201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傳「潑墨女孩」董瑤瓊再被關進精神病院】","createTime":"2021-02-09T14:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T17:33:45.000Z","uid":126919,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9187c9746aeaa6c852f39f716459b36b5093d520","tid":2401201,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"2018 年在上海向中共總書記習近平畫像潑墨的「潑墨女孩」董瑤瓊，據報再被當局關押在精神病院。流亡藝術家華湧周一晚（8 日）在其推特透露，董瑤瓊在上周六（6 日）再被當局關押於株洲市第三病院。<br />\n<br />\n今次是董瑤瓊第三次被關在精神病院，華湧呼籲外界關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月，董瑤瓊被送往精神病院治療一年半後出院，她當時神情痴呆，且不願意說話，與之前活潑的性格相比， 簡直是判若兩人，加上她身形比入院前浮腫，懷疑她在精神病院期間被餵藥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/5012658052142006/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F454004001340790%2Fposts%2F5012658052142006%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=c8a201de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/454004001340790/posts/5012658052142006/</a>"},{"pid":"cb252b7a213eaf326980289f1c8dd126ee149e5a","tid":2401201,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9288c5a17067c4a4ad82f18ded55432b9729aa9d","tid":2401201,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb252b7a213eaf326980289f1c8dd126ee149e5a","tid":2401201,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"想唔癲都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\"